#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: multiline text field through ingestion. _chemical_formula.sum is stored
# as a semicolon-delimited multiline string. The text-field transformation
# pipeline (prefix removal, line unfolding) runs in the IR layer; the ingestion
# layer receives the already-transformed string and must store it as-is.
#
# The CHEMICAL_FORMULA table columns, sum, iupac, analytical, and moiety have the same value.
#
# Dictionary: cif_core

data_test_multiline_formula
_cell.length_a    5.000
_cell.length_b    5.000
_cell.length_c    5.000
_cell.angle_alpha 90
_cell.angle_beta  90
_cell.angle_gamma 90
_chemical_formula.sum
;Fe2 O3
;
_chemical_formula.iupac
;prefix>\
prefix>Fe2 O3
;
_chemical_formula.analytical "Fe2 O3"
_chemical_formula.moiety     '''Fe2 O3'''
_chemical_formula.weight 159.69
